The following is a list of primary authors and contributors for Crazy Eddie's
GUI System Mk-2.


CEGUI Team
---------
James O'Sullivan (_mental_)
Tomas Lindquist Olsen (lindquist)
Paul D Turner (crayzed / CrazyEddie)
